      <p>
      Divisions: It seems even the ancient scholars were fairly confused 
      about what <p:ac>等</p:ac> divisions actually meant; see 
      <s:cite-group>
        <s:cite key="Baxter 1992" pages="42" />
        <s:cite key="Táng 2016" pages="57" />
      </s:cite-group>.
      Only in early modern times did scholars start to figure out that
      divisions were ordered on the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vowel#Backness">vowel's backness</a>.
      </p>.

